## Build & Test

```bash
cd shared-ui
swift build       # Builds platform-independent parts on Linux/macOS
swift test        # Runs parser + regex pattern tests (113 tests)

# Full build (requires macOS with Xcode for SwiftUI/UIKit components)
# SwiftUI components are conditionally compiled with #if canImport(SwiftUI)
```

## Architecture

- **Platform-independent:** `CoverFlowKernel`, `MarkdownBlockParser`,
  `MarkdownSectionParser`, `MarkdownTheme` вҖ“ build on Linux and macOS
- **SwiftUI-dependent:** All view components (`CoverFlow`, `ActionButton`,
  `GlassOverlayScaffold`, `MarkdownDocumentView`, `MarkdownText`) вҖ“
  require macOS/iOS with SwiftUI, guarded by `#if canImport(SwiftUI)`
- **UIKit-dependent:** `MarkdownEditorView`, `MarkdownTextStorage` вҖ“
  require iOS, guarded by `#if canImport(UIKit)`
- **Zero external dependencies:** Consistent with mono-repo policy

